name: [NVIDIA] Triton Inference Server (24.01)
description:
Triton Inference Server is open source software that lets teams deploy trained AI models from any framework, from local or cloud storage and on any GPU- or CPU-based infrastructure in the cloud, data center, or embedded devices.

This is the standard py3 image with support for Tensorflow, PyTorch, TensorRT, ONNX and OpenVINO models.
